:sweat_smile: :sweat_smile: :sweat_smile: 

Yup I’ll raise a ticket
This was discussed before, wasn't the decision made that recipebooks wouldnt be removed?

There are two types of .ibrecipebook files - custom UIs and what we referred to as Recipebooks, which were a collection of cards that described a project. We deprecated the latter, not the former. I'm assuming this is a custom UI?

There's no reason I can think of off the top of my head that it would work on the latest release, 24.07, but not on 24.04. I can help debug though

Thanks @Jessica.
@Yatharth Vardan can you find time with Jessica on this?
